sourcesContent:
import { VueFormGenerator } from "vue-form-generator"

export default {
    groups: [
        {
            label: "Product Details",
            fields: [
                {
                    type: 'input',
                    inputType: 'text',
                    label: 'Product Name',
                    model: 'productName',
                    required: true,
                    validator: ['string', 'required']
                },
                {
                    type: 'input',
                    inputType: 'select',
                    label: 'Product Group',
                    model: 'productGroup',
                    required: true,
                    validator: ['string', 'required']
                },
                {
                    type: 'input',
                    inputType: 'text',
                    label: 'Bag Size (in kgs)',
                    model: 'bagSize',
                    required: true,
                    validator: ['string', 'required']
                },
                {
                    type: 'input',
                    inputType: 'text',
                    label: 'Computed Product Name',
                    model: 'computedProductName',
                    required: true,
                    validator: ['string', 'required']
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            label: "Charges and rents",
            fields: [
                {
                    type: 'input',
                    inputType: 'text',
                    label: 'Hamali per bag',
                    model: 'hamaliPerBag',
                    required: true,
                    validator: ['string', 'required']
                },
                {
                    type: 'input',
                    inputType: 'text',
                    label: 'Platform Coolie per bag',
                    model: 'platformCooliePerBag',
                    required: true,
                    validator: ['string', 'required']
                },
                {
                    type: 'input',
                    inputType: 'text',
                    label: 'Kata Coolie per bag',
                    model: 'kataCooliePerBag',
                    required: true,
                    validator: ['string', 'required']
                },
                {
                    type: 'input',
                    inputType: 'text',
                    label: 'Mamullu per bag',
                    model: 'mamulluPerBag',
                    required: true,
                    validator: ['string', 'required']
                },
                {
                    type: 'input',
                    inputType: 'text',
                    label: 'Monthly Rent per bag',
                    model: 'monthlyRentPerBag',
                    required: true,
                    validator: ['string', 'required']
                },
                {
                    type: 'input',
                    inputType: 'text',
                    label: 'Yeraly rent per kg',
                    model: 'yearlyRentPerkg',
                    required: true,
                    validator: ['string', 'required']
                },
                {
                    type: 'input',
                    inputType: 'text',
                    label: 'Computed Yearly Rent per bag',
                    model: 'computedYeralyRentPerBag',
                    required: true,
                    validator: ['string', 'required']
                },
                {
                    type: 'input',
                    inputType: 'text',
                    label: 'Yearly Rent per bag',
                    model: 'yearlyRentPerBag',
                    required: true,
                    validator: ['string', 'required']
                },
                {
                    type: 'input',
                    inputType: 'text',
                    label: 'Insurance per bag',
                    model: 'insurancePerBag',
                    required: true,
                    validator: ['string', 'required']
                }
            ]
        }
    ]
}
